== Jinos ==
Balchanv ek randpachi pod’dhot, zo [[nustem]], [[sungttam]], vo [[dukrachem mas]], eka [[mosaleant]] ani pormollttolea tomatanchea ani [[mirsangan]]<nowiki/>chea sosant korpant ieta.<ref name="ThomasKarafin2009">{{cite book|author1=Amelia Thomas|author2=Amy Karafin|title=Goa and Mumbai|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=ZxY69WvM5o0C&pg=PA60|accessdate=14 August 2012|date=1 October 2009|publisher=Lonely Planet|isbn=978-1-74104-894-0|pages=60–}}</ref> To ek [[lonnchea]] sarko asa ani to zaiteach adim portun gorom kornastana korunk zata.

Paromporik balchanvant ek kharea [[sungttan]]<nowiki/>cho kholl vaportat zaka [[Konknni]]<nowiki/>nt ''[[gallmo]]'' mhonnttat,

Tachea jinosant [[sungttam]], [[tel]], barik katorlolo [[piav]], [[tomatam]], losunnacho kholl vo lovongam, [[alea]]<nowiki/>cho kholl vo alem, sukeo [[tambddeo mirsango]], [[jirem]], [[sansvam]], [[tikhi]], [[lovongam]], [[sakhor]], [[vinagr]] ani [[mitth]] hancho aspav asta.<ref name="Balchao" />

== Toiari ==
Toiar korpachi pod’dhotichem vornnon sangta ki poilim sungttam nitoll korunk zai tanchem sut kaddlea uprant, [[mitth]] lavun eka vhodd aidonant kuxik dovrunk zai. [[Tambddeo mursango]], [[jirem]], [[sansvam]], [[lovongam]] ani [[tikhi]] eka sukhea toveacher pormoll iesor bhazunk za.i Uprant tem thondd zavnk dovrunk zai. Alem, lossunn ani bhazlolo mosalo pittho vinagrin mellovn tacho kholl korunk zai. Tel gorom korun, sungttam tantunt misoll korunk zai ani firovn  datt zaisor bhazunk zai. Magir, toveacher piav bhazunk zai. Piav puddi rongacho zatoch, tomatam ghalunk zai ani mov zaisor bhazunk zai. Mosalea-vinagricho kholl tantunt sakhre ani mittha sangata ghalunk zai, Hea uprant tel, mosaleantlean bhair soro poriant bhazunk zai, sungttam ghalun hem sogllem  2-3 minut randunk zai.<ref name="Balchao" />

Balchanv chodd korun gorom, sadea ukddea xitant vaporpant ieta. To frijint dovorpak zai ani chodd kallant [[frij]]<nowiki/>int dovrunk zata.

